<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=98649574093146></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98649574093146><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=3&mid=98649574093146>RE: Should I Start Over?</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=3&mid=98649574093146#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=9543><span id=Scholar>Landrion</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>31 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Apr 5th 2:35 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>There is no way in that formula to get a negative result.<br><br>Let me break down the formula to make it simpler and more understandable (hopefully), start with the innermost parenthesis.  For the purposes of this explanation we will use Garren as the example with a few made up numbers to fill in what we don't know.<br><br>level=13<br>str=100<br>weaponskill=70 (this is max for 13, as (level*5)+5 gives us)<br>weapondamage=6 (his fists at level 13 are 6dmg/36dly)<br><br>The formula we will use is:<br><br>max=weapondamage*((str+weaponskill)/100)<br><br>(we won't bother with the part after that because you don't even get a 1 until level 28 as that part of it is meant to be a bonus)<br><br>so:<br><br>str+weaponskill<br>100+70 gives us 170<br><br>/100 gives us a player factor of 1.7<br><br>weapondamage *<br>we multiply the weapondamage by our factor<br>6*1.7<br><br>so our max then is 10 (10.2)<br><br>I'll plug all the numbers into the formula so we can see it:<br><br>max=weapondamage * ((str+weaponskill)/100)<br><br>so...<br><br>10.2=6 * ((100+70)/100)<br><br>So now this is clear as crystal or more like mud.  I hope the former is true.<br><br>Zzaarno Painmaker<br>Monk of the 22nd Season<br>Court of Pain<br>Tholuxe-Paells<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
